race.description: Share Bets With Tabtouch Bet Loop Handicap
race.comment: MAGNIQUE (3) was strong late over 1000m last start and stepping back up to 1200m is a big tick. She pushed a smart one here two back in stronger company and that looks hot form for a race of this calibre. Faithfull hops back on board and she can make every post a winner. JUST SAINT JAMES (1) flew late in the Batavia at Geraldton and will find this a little easier. His fresh win over 1100m was strong and suggested he's in for a good campaign. Can sit closer from the draw today and put his best foot forward. HEY PINO (4) has been flying late in recent events, bumping into a smart one here two back. She drops right down in the weights again today and if she can settle a touch closer from the draw today, she'll be hard to hold out. SALTY MISS (12) bolted in fresh at Bunbury and can go on with the job here with improvement likely. RETURN OF THE MACH (10) was too good over 1000m fresh and can repeat the dose out in trip second-up.
